parameters.name: userId
parameters.description: User numeric identifier. Filter managed credentials by specific user.

parameters.name: search
parameters.description: Filter search parameter. Supports free text search on `userName`, `firstName + lastName`, and keywords: `is:missing`, `is:added`.

parameters.name: max
parameters.description: Maximum number of results to return. Default: `20`.

parameters.name: offset
parameters.description: Number of results to skip for pagination. Default: `0`.
